actions.message:
```
.say (whatthebotdosay) let the bot send a message
.time get the current time of the bot
.stats get the stats of the bot
.info same as .stats
.uptime same as .stats
.ping same as .stats
.play (youryoutubevideo) let the bot play music from youtube
.stop stop playing music
.resume play music continues
.leave the bot leave your voice channel
.google (searchongoogle) search on google
.serverinfo get the info of the current server
.meme send a random meme
.createrole (newrolename) create a new role
.setservername (newservername) set the server of the current 
.add (number1) (number2) math adding task
.clear (amounttodeltemessages) delete messages
.invite get the bot invite link
.ban (playerthebecomebanned) ban a player
.weather (city/country) get the weather
```
